         <abstract id="aspace_068c200bdcbf170f4747d946fe5e990d">The records consist of correspondence, working files, orders, printed material, and financial records of the Publications Office, Yale University Library. Topics include the publication projects, Research Libraries Group, and Systems Office projects.</abstract>
